<p class="meta">Published: May 22, 2026 | Reading time: 10 minutes</p>



<p>DogeKing ($DKING) has emerged as one of the most talked-about meme coins on the Solana blockchain in 2026. With its royal-themed branding, active community, and growing ecosystem, more investors than ever are looking to add $DKING to their portfolios. But if you're new to crypto - or new to Solana - the buying process can feel intimidating.</p>



<p>This guide walks you through every single step, from signing up on Binance (the best exchange for this purchase) to securing your tokens with a Ledger hardware wallet. We'll cover everything in plain English so you can buy $DKING with confidence.</p>



