<h2 id="frequently-asked-questions">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>



<div class="faq-item">

<h3>Can I buy DogeKing ($DKING) directly with USD or a credit card?</h3>

<p>No, you cannot buy $DKING directly with fiat currency. You must first buy SOL (Solana's native token) on a centralized exchange like Binance, then swap your SOL for $DKING on a decentralized exchange like Jupiter or Raydium. This two-step process is standard for most Solana-based meme coins and ensures you're interacting directly with on-chain liquidity.</p>

