<div class="faq-item">

<h3>What is the minimum amount of DogeKing ($DKING) I can buy in 2026?</h3>

<p>There is no minimum purchase amount on decentralized exchanges like Jupiter. You can buy as little as one $DKING token if you want. However, you need a small amount of SOL in your wallet to cover Solana transaction fees, which are typically less than $0.001 per swap. Most investors start with at least 0.1 to 1 SOL to make the fees negligible relative to their purchase.</p>

</div>



<div class="faq-item">

<h3>Is DogeKing ($DKING) safe to buy, and how can I avoid scams?</h3>

<p>DogeKing ($DKING) is a community-driven meme coin on the Solana blockchain. To buy safely: always use the official $DKING contract address from DogeKing's verified Twitter/X or Discord channels; double-check URLs before connecting your wallet to any dApp; never share your 12-word seed phrase with anyone; avoid "free airdrop" sites that ask you to connect your wallet; and consider storing long-term holdings on a Ledger hardware wallet for cold storage protection. No legitimate project will ever ask for your private keys.</p>

</div>



